!!!
%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=utf-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}/
  %body
    Hi Betsy,
    %br
    Here are my hours for last week.
    %br
    %table
      %thead
        %tr
          %th Day
          %th Start
          %th End
          %th Length
      %tbody
        - @shifts.each do |shift|
          %tr
            %td= shift.date.strftime '%A'
            %td= shift.time
            %td= shift.end_time.strftime('%l:%M %P')
            %td= shift.length
        %tr
          %th{colspan: 2} Total
          %th{colspan: 2}= @shifts.sum :length

    %br
    Thanks,
    %br
    David
